gomodel:SYNGO_3793  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 5: Reversal of LTP impairment in Ube3A null (AS) mice by apamin, an SK2 channel blocker shows that Ube3A depletion leads to higher membrane expression of SK2 leading to LTP impairments.. Experimental description: M&M: Hippocampal neurons were prepared from embryonic day 18 (E18) mouse embryos, bred with UBE3Am/p+ female and male mice, as described previously (Qin et al., 2009)." ;
